attributes.description: Banco Products (India) Ltd manufactures and supplies engine cooling modules and systems for automotive and industrial applications in both the domestic and international markets. It was Incorporated in 1961, promoted by Mr. Mehul K. Patel who has more than 40 years of experience in the automotive industry [1]
